creator: HD Wallpaper themes
descriptionHtml:
Five wallpaper is the perfect wallpaper for all nature lovers. Our app inspires optimism. With Flowers live wallpaper you can choose between 4 HD images featuring blossom, daisy, gerbera daisies, anthurium, violets and many others.

You can also set all the backgrounds you see in Flowers live wallpaper as normal phone wallpapers.

Flowers live wallpaper is suitable for the Summer season.

Activation:
(1) Press "Apply" button
(2) Press "Set Wallpaper" button
(3) Summer flowers live wallpaper is now active on your home screen.

**** If the above doesn't work you will find Flowers live wallpaper in the phone's live wallpaper selection. You can usually find "Live Wallpapers" category on your phone when changing the wallpaper from your launcher.

Customize options:
(1) Change the flowers that animate your screen and adjust their type. Choose between: daisy, gerbera daisy, anthurium, violet.
(2) Change the wallpaper. All backgrounds are HD and will look beautiful on your android phone home screen.

Other features:
• Flowers live wallpaper is optimized for most android devices.
• Wallpapers look crisp, HD and are beautiful.
• Enjoy the best wallpapers for your phone.
• Suitable backgrounds for girls and boys.
• Looks great on black and white android phones

title: Flowers live wallpaper

creator: HD Wallpaper themes
descriptionHtml:
This app is the perfect wallpaper for all nature lovers. Our app inspires optimism and spring or summer season. HD images featuring blossom, daisy, gerbera daisies, anthurium, violets and many others.
You can also set all the backgrounds you see in this app as normal phone wallpapers.

What you will find in this app:
- Almost 30 backgrounds.
- HD wallpapers with various animations.
- Unique and exclusive live wallpapers that you will not find anywhere else.

Features in this app:
- 3D magic sparkling glitter effect, tilt your phone after you enable it and the magic will happen, the glitter effect will sparkle all over the screen
- more than 10 different particles
- more than 10 different animations
- Magic touch: highly requested, now you have a live wallpaper that you can play with. We added 5 different touch effects. You can always disable this feature.
- Various options for the particles. Maybe you want more particles on your screen? Or you want them to move faster? Or maybe you just want them to be bigger.
- Cool and high definition wallpapers suitable for the size of your screen will mentain high visual quality on small or large phones even tablets.
- We update our apps frequently to keep your screen stunning with new wallpapers
- Add your own image or photo and customize your wallpaper as you wish
- Optimized for Super IPS, AMOLED, OLED phone screens.
- Easy to preview and set your favourite wallpaper, fast UI and quick loading.
- We expanding our app, when you have some time just open the app and scroll through it to find new backgrounds.
- Battery will not be affected by our apps.
We hope you enjoy our redesigned app with fresh backgrounds!

Click "Apply" and "Set wallpaper" in order to complete the activation process.
If that doesn't work, apply this background from your phone's live wallpapers list.
